=== 真核生物啟動子 ===
[[真核生物|真核生物]]啟動子是極端的分化及很難表現其特徵。它們一般處於[[基因|基因]]的上游及有著遠離[[轉錄|轉錄]]起始點的調控元件。轉錄複合物可以引起[[去氧核糖核酸|去氧核糖核酸]]（DNA）向自己屈曲，以容許放置調控序列。很多真核生物啟動子，但不是全部，都包含一個[[TATA盒|TATA盒]]（序列TATAAA）會與[[TATA結合蛋白|TATA結合蛋白]]結合，以協助形成[[RNA聚合酶|RNA聚合酶]]轉錄複合物。<ref>{{cite journal en | author = Smale ST, Kadonaga JT | year = 2003 | title = The RNA polymerase II core promoter | journal = Annu Rev Biochem | volume = 72 | pages = 449-479 | id = PMID 12651739 | url = http://www.lpt.ens.fr/~monasson/Houches/Kadonaga/CorePromoterAnnuRev2003.pdf | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20061031140737/http://www.lpt.ens.fr/~monasson/Houches/Kadonaga/CorePromoterAnnuRev2003.pdf | archivedate = 2006-10-31 | access-date = 2006-11-17 }}</ref>TATA盒一般會處於非常接近轉錄起始點（通常於50個[[鹼基對|鹼基對]]以內）。

真核生物啟動子調控序列一般與[[轉錄因子|轉錄因子]]結合，當中涉及形成轉錄複合物。一個例子是E盒（序列CACGTG），它會與[[鹼性螺旋-環-螺旋|鹼性螺旋-環-螺旋]]（bHLH）的轉錄因子結合。<ref>{{cite journal en | author = Levine M, Tjian R | year = 2003 | title = Transcription regulation and animal diversity | journal = Nature | volume = 424 | issue = 6945 | pages = 147-151 | id = PMID 12853946 | url = http://bioweb.usc.edu/courses/2003-fall/documents/bisc320-gp_article1.pdf | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070122123329/http://bioweb.usc.edu/courses/2003-fall/documents/bisc320-gp_article1.pdf | archivedate = 2007-01-22 | access-date = 2006-11-17 }}</ref>

== 結合 ==
啟動子序列（P）與[[σ因子|σ因子]][[RNA聚合酶|RNA聚合酶]]複合物（R）的結合涉及兩個步驟：
:<math>\mbox{R} + \mbox{P} \leftrightarrow \mbox{RP}_{\mbox{(closed)}}</math>
:<math>\mbox{RP}_{\mbox{(closed)}} \rightarrow \mbox{RP}_{\mbox{(open)}}</math>

